OL,5,G0205 Wentworth: The Final Sentence
OL,6,     FAfter a near fatal stabbing of
OL,7,     FAllie returns to Wentworth
OL,8,     Fgrappling with permanent injuries.
OL,9,     FMeanwhile, Ferguson finds it
OL,10,     Fincreasingly difficult to control
OL,11,     Fher desire for revenge.
OL,12,G0310 Wentworth: The Final Sentence
OL,13,     FDetermined to find out who killed
OL,14,     FReb, Lou finds herself comforted
OL,15,     Fby Marie, not realising Marie's
OL,16,     Fpart in the conspiracy, and that
OL,17,     FReb's killer pays with their life.
